  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA22">
<l>ariya teḷitāku māṟṟalāṉ māṟṟip</l>
<l>peruka muyalvāraip peṟṟāṟ – kariyatōr</l>
<l>veṇkōṭṭu mālyāṉai veṉṟimuṭit taṉṟē</l>
<l>taṇkōṭṭu māmalarāṟ ṟāḻntu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What is difficult becomes easy, if one finds those who make</l>
<l>an effort to change [and] improve by [their own] strength.</l>
<l>The unique huge elephant that is black with white tusks accomplished victory,</l>
<l>bowing low with a big blossom on a cool twig.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
